      <title>马士基、赫伯罗特计划 2025 年启航南非航线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/maersk-hapag-lloyd-plan-to-sail-south-of-africa-into-2025-m21n7zwo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两家集装箱运输巨头马士基航运和赫伯罗特航运开始进行船舶共享合作，并计划从非洲南部开始合作航行，这表明他们预计红海在 2025 年之前仍然不安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/maersk-hapag-lloyd-plan-to-sail-south-of-africa-into-2025-m21n7zwo</guid>
