      <title>中国人民币垃圾公司债券将创十年来最大单日跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/china-s-yuan-junk-corporate-bonds-set-for-worst-day-in-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者期待政府出台更多措施提振经济，中国在岸高收益债券市场正遭遇多年来最糟糕的交易日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/china-s-yuan-junk-corporate-bonds-set-for-worst-day-in-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 08:29:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富时罗素将希腊股票评级提升至发达市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/greek-stocks-on-path-to-developed-market-upgrade-by-ftse-russell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着希腊逐渐摆脱长达十年的债务危机并恢复正常，希腊股市距离再次加入发达市场行列又近了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/greek-stocks-on-path-to-developed-market-upgrade-by-ftse-russell</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 08:28:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称大众银行正考虑收购已故创始人家族在 LPI 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/public-bank-is-said-to-consider-buying-late-founder-s-family-stake-in-lpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，大众银行有限公司 (Public Bank Bhd.) 正在考虑收购其已故创始人郑鸿标 (Teh Hong Piow) 家族在 Lonpac Insurance Bhd. 所有者的股份。]]></description>
